00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Understanding how much time people are spending on your site or

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:08.289
pages can help you unlock crucial user behavior.

00:00:08.289 --> 00:00:12.660
Especially, when you're a publisher who relies on advertising revenue,

00:00:12.660 --> 00:00:15.824
getting people to spend time on your site is essential,

00:00:15.824 --> 00:00:19.289
and the time spent usually correlates with revenue.

00:00:19.289 --> 00:00:24.469
Let's take a look at how time is measured using Google Analytics.

